I '''Miriam Defensor Santiago''' (mibait '''Miriam Palma Defensor''' anyang Junio 15, 1945) metung yang mepiling Ukum ning [[International Criminal Court]] ampong kayanib ning [[Senado ning Filipinas]]. Metung yang abogada, sadyang ukum, ampong propesor ning leying pang-punbatas ampong leying internasional (constitutional law and international law). Migsilbi yang Komisyonado ning Pamaglipat ampong Pamagpalwal (Commissioner of the Bureau of Immigration and Deportation) anyang 1988, ampong Kalihim ning Repormang Agraryo manibat and the Secretary of the Philippines' [[Sakdalan ning Repormang Agraryo]] manibat 1989 anggang 1991. Ya ing talatátag ampong kasalukuyang pekapun ning [[panglibutad-wanan]] a [[People's Reform Party]] a ka-alyadu ning sadyang pamuntuk [[Gloria Macapagal-Arroyo]],<ref name="newsflash.org">http://www.newsflash.org/2003/05/hl/hl019623.htm MIRIAM  AS 12TH, COMPLETES GMA'S K-4 SENATORIAL SLATE January 9, 2004</ref> at metung yang Laureado ning [[Ramon Magsaysay Award]] para king serbisyong pangkapamahalan.

Tinagal ya para king katungkulan a [[Pamunuk ning Filipinas]] anyang 1992 i Defensor Santiago;ya ing mumuna king pamamilang kareng botu kareng mumunang limang aldo, oneng bandang tawli mesambut ya king pilatan a ala pang metung a milyung botu kareng atlung pulu't anam a milyung (36,000,000) a botu. Sasabyan dang mika maleparan a pirait king kampanya, at mika kapansin-pansin a blackout king kuryenti kaybat da reng mumunang limang aldo. Minapag yang protesta, dapot tebili re ini uli ning teknikalidad anyang tinagal ya at sinambut para king pwestu king Senado.<ref name="senate.gov.ph">{{cite web|url=http://www.senate.gov.ph/senators/sen_bio/santiago_bio.asp |title=Senator Miriam Defensor Santiago - Senate of the Philippines |publisher=Senate.gov.ph |date= |accessdate=2011-03-13}}</ref>

Maralas deng babalita i Miriam kareng internasional a pahayagan uli ning kayang charisma, makuleng pangatau ampong kasebyan a nakaugne kaya, anya gad neng lalapitan ning balita.Anyang 1997, pinili ne ning metung a magasin king Australia antimong metung kareng mayupayang diling bábai king yatu (one of "The 100 Most Powerful Women in the World"). Kareng tawling banwa, Mas bayu kaniti, megi yang manimunang talapagsalita (keynote speaker) ning kapulungang internasional laban king korupsyon king Sydney, Australia. Antimong senador, ya ing migdala ampong minantabe king pangapasar na king Senado ning Filipinas ning UN Convention Against Corruption.

